sentences: Wilt "Tallpree" Cambridge (born 29 July 1973) is a Grenadian soca artist.

He initially began performing as a reggae dancehall artist in the late 1980s and made the switch to becoming a soca artist the late 90s. His first stage name was Mr. Evilus, but by the time he began singing the popular "Jab Jab" â€“ infused music soca enthusiasts have come to expect from him, he changed his name to Tallpree.
